<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看了看走廊。一个人也没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她赶紧从背包里拿出跳绳，在走廊里跳起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！快停下。不能在室内跳绳！” 有人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转过身，看到五年级的管理班长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是从哪里跑出来的？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我正要去体育馆。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在室内跳绳要报告给校长。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看着他写下记录，叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“弗拉尼校长很快就会知道了。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但走进体育馆时，她笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师正拿着一条长长的、橙色的跳绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪边跳边唱：“我喜欢咖啡，我喜欢茶，我要尼娜跟我跳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来了！” 尼娜大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她放下背包，拿出绳子，和莉琪一起跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢咖啡，我喜欢茶，我要贾森跟我跳！” 莉琪唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森拿起跳绳想要加入。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们出去跳吧，孩子们。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“记住，在走廊里要走，不能跳。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都知道今天是跳绳日。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会轮流跳绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，我们需要两个人摇绳子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜用手肘碰了碰波比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪用手肘碰了碰贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来摇绳子吧。” 男生们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。尼娜和莉琪还要唱跳绳歌，对不对？” 老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，你们可能已经会了。” 尼娜对男生们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你准备好了吗，尼娜？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜跳了起来。“准备好了！我练习很久了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们从‘尼娜、尼娜，转转圈’开始。好吗？” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生们和雪莉老师点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜、尼娜，转转圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜、尼娜，摸摸地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜、尼娜，抬抬脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜、尼娜，你真棒。” 他们唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，到你了。” 贾森边摇边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，我来了！我们唱 ‘草莓蛋糕’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪边说边往里跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“草莓蛋糕，奶油在上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告诉我们谁在你的心里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，你喜欢贾森！” 尼娜大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有！” 莉琪喘着气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是大家都看到她脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，最后一轮。我们唱‘咖啡和茶’吧。” 她赶紧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“摇绳子吧。” 尼娜对男生们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到弗拉尼校长正走向停车场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢咖啡，我喜欢茶，我要弗拉尼校长跟我跳！” 女生们唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>校长很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她把包放下，跳了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在外面跳绳更有意思，对不对，尼娜？” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>